"With no ``values`` only the mesh wireframe is drawn. Passing ``Dict[str, "
"torch.Tensor]`` produces a static multi-panel figure; passing ``Dict[str,"
" List[torch.Tensor]]`` produces an mp4/gif animation (one frame per list "
"element)."
msgstr ""

#: 5c13581e0b1846c7a08d87c0a9b5ad4e of tensormesh.mesh.mesh.Mesh.plot:8
msgid ""
"the values to plot, if None, only plot the mesh if ``Dict[str, "
"torch.Tensor]``, a static subplots will be plotted, the key is the name "
"of the subplot, the value is of shape :math:`[|\\mathcal V|]`, where "
":math:`|\\mathcal V|` is the number of interpolation nodes if ``Dict[str,"
" List[torch.Tensor]]``, a mp4/gif will be plotted, the key is the name of"
" the subplot, each item in the list is of shape :math:`[|\\mathcal V|]`, "
"where :math:`|\\mathcal V|` is the number of interpolation nodes default:"
" None"
msgstr ""

#: ff154c79421d4fa1ab33680830a2563d of tensormesh.mesh.mesh.Mesh.plot:13
msgid ""
"the path to save the plot, if None, it will not be saved if the "
"``values`` is passed in as ``Dict[str, List[torch.Tensor]]``, the "
"``save_path`` must endswith '.mp4' or '.gif' default: None"
msgstr ""

#: 179da8170482458493e72b6b6189aab2 of tensormesh.mesh.mesh.Mesh.plot:17
msgid ""
"the time interval between each frame, only used when ``values`` is passed"
" in as ``Dict[str, List[torch.Tensor]]`` default: None"
msgstr ""

#: ee12c529d3044b758039a10f9dbe07eb of tensormesh.mesh.mesh.Mesh.plot:20
msgid ""
"whether to overlay the mesh wireframe (and, at ``order >= 2``, the "
"interpolation nodes) on top of the colour-filled field. Only takes effect"
" when ``values`` is given. default: False"
msgstr ""

#: 4856c610a98d4f40820f1483a341ecc5 of tensormesh.mesh.mesh.Mesh.plot:25
msgid ""
"whether to fix the color limits across all frames, only used when "
"``values`` is passed in as ``Dict[str, List[torch.Tensor]]``. If True, "
"the color limits are determined by the global min and max across all "
"frames, ensuring a consistent colorbar throughout the animation. default:"
" False"
msgstr ""

#: 565fcbc7302f45dcbb6e513f7c259064 of tensormesh.mesh.mesh.Mesh.plot:29
